Lsdvd is a c application for reading the contents of a DVD and printing 
the contents to your terminal.

Information provided by lsdvd about a whole bunch of things:

    * Name of the disc
    * Number of tracks
    * Length, format, aspect of each track
    * Format, language, number of channels, contents etc... of each audio 
      track
    * Language and contents of each subtitle
    * Other stuff!
